ure request is a bit difficult to read because the sub section titles and bodies have almost the same font color and size:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"869\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-05-19 at 18 55 12\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/17039389/169266862-af0c9b28-e77f-4563-ba73-374c68d17c21.png\">\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\n\r\nWe can add `> ` to each sub section title:\r\n\r\n```diff\r\ndiff --git a/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/feature_request_template.yaml b/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/feature_request_template.yaml\r\nindex 31e910919..7f68c424c 100644\r\n--- a/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/feature_request_template.yaml\r\n+++ b/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/feature_request_template.yaml\r\n@@ -36,13 +36,13 @@ body:\r\n         - Why is this use case valuable to support for your project(s) or organization?\r\n         - Why is it currently difficult to achieve this use case? (please be as specific as possible about why related MLflow features and components are insufficient)\r\n       value: |\r\n-        #### What is the use case for this feature?\r\n+        > #### What is the use case for this feature?\r\n \r\n-        #### Why is this use case valuable to support for MLflow users in general?\r\n+        > #### Why is this use case valuable to support for MLflow users in general?\r\n \r\n-        #### Why is this use case valuable to support for your project(s) or organization?\r\n+        > #### Why is this use case valuable to support for your project(s) or organization?\r\n \r\n-        #### Why is it currently difficult to achieve this use case?\r\n+        > #### Why is it currently difficult to achieve this use case?\r\n     validations:\r\n       required: true\r\n   - type: textarea\r\n```\r\n\r\n<img width=\"869\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-05-19 at 18 54 52\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/17039389/169267251-03fa336f-42c0-4833-837b-25ee7ac8a97f.png\">\r\n\r\n","closed_by":{"login":"harupy","id":17039389,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE3MDM5Mzg5","avatar_url":"https://avatars